Frequently Asked Questions

How old is Dwight Howard?

Dwight Howard is 39 years old.

Where was Dwight Howard born?

Dwight Howard was born in Atlanta, Georgia.

When was Dwight Howard born?

Dwight Howard was born on December 8, 1985.

How tall is Dwight Howard?

Dwight Howard is 6-10 (208 cm) tall.

How much did Dwight Howard weigh when playing?

Dwight Howard weighed 265 lbs (120 kg) when playing.

Is Dwight Howard in the Hall of Fame?

Dwight Howard was inducted to the Hall of Fame as a Player in 2025 (Full List) .

When was Dwight Howard drafted?

Dwight Howard was drafted by Orlando Magic, 1st round (1st pick, 1st overall), 2004 NBA Draft.

What position did Dwight Howard play?

Center and Power Forward.

When did Dwight Howard retire?

Dwight Howard last played in 2022.

What is Dwight Howard's net worth?

Dwight Howard made at least $247,888,692 playing professional basketball.

How much did Dwight Howard make?

Dwight Howard made $23,500,000 in 2018.

What did Dwight Howard average?

Dwight Howard averaged 15.7 points, 11.8 rebounds, and 1.3 assists per game.

How many rings does Dwight Howard have?

Dwight Howard won one championship.

What is Dwight Howard's Instagram account?

Dwight Howard is on Instagram at dwighthoward.

What schools did Dwight Howard attend?

Dwight Howard attended Southwest Atlanta Christian Academy in Atlanta, Georgia.

What are Dwight Howard's nicknames?

Superman, D12, The Daily Double are nicknames for Dwight Howard.
